So define:
	•	how ids look
	•	how users refer to artifacts
	•	short vs long names

This ties into your artifact system vision:
everything is reproducible and addressable
￼

⸻

8. minimal parser spec (bridge to C)

You do not need full grammar yet, but define:
	•	line = tokens split by space
	•	first token = verb or key
	•	colon splits key value
